description.en: This beautiful table is made by light wood. Good for bright living rooms and covered terraces. Two powerful legs surprise with their design and will not leave anyone indifferent.
This unique table is well suited for cozy gatherings of 6-8 people. The unique structure of wood and color will not leave you on the sidelines. It is very comfortable and ergonomic

This unique table looks like stone from a distance, but no, it is made of light wood. The unique design of the legs is made by the best craftsmen. And the unique texture of the surface does not absorb stains and you can not be afraid to use it for family dinners.
